---

## Rationalization Table

| What You're Thinking                                       | What You Should Do                                                               |
| ---------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| "This task is trivial, I don't need to re-read the design" | Re-read. Context compression loses details. 30s of reading saves 30min of rework |
